# Research Institute Rules (科研院所行业规则)

Scope: research-pack and related AppPacks

## Domain Knowledge

- Core entities: Product (5-phase), BOMNode (3-tier), Component (关键件/重要件), ProductionOrder, QualityInspection, NCR (NonConformance), ChangeRequest (ECR/ECO), TestReport (6 types), Supplier, Material, ProjectMilestone, ResearchTask.
- Key metrics: first-pass yield (一次交验合格率), production plan completion rate, NCR closure timeliness, milestone on-time delivery rate, supplier quality rating, equipment availability.
- Data sources: QMS (质量管理系统), PLM (产品全生命周期管理), MES, ERP.

## Compliance Constraints

- NCR (不合格品报告) closure must follow "五步法归零" procedure.
- Engineering change (ECR/ECO) requires multi-level approval workflow.
- Test reports for critical components require dual-signature verification.
- All quality data retention: minimum 10 years (国防科工局要求).
- AI cannot auto-approve any quality-related action — always HITL.

## Data Security

- Product design data (BOM, test results): TOP-SECRET classification.
- Supplier evaluation data: CONFIDENTIAL.
- Project milestone data: INTERNAL minimum.
- All data access logged with full audit trail (regulatory requirement).
